snippet.title: AEW: Fight Forever | Switchblade Tournament Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Guns out! Bullet Club Gold's own "Switchblade" Jay White is entering the AEW: Fight Forever ring!
The Switchblade Tournament Pack is now available with Jay White, an all-new tournament mode, new moves, and new premium music tracks.

This content is part of Season Pass 4 which includes:
3 new wrestlers, 2 new maps including the Haunted Forest map ,a New Tournament Mode, 30 new move-sets, 52 new skin and attire options, and 5 new music tracks
